Package: process-tracker
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},${python:Depends},python-daemon,python-psutil(>=0.6.1),python-lockfile,python-apscheduler
Description: extensible process tracking utility
 process-tracker is an extensible process tracking utility.
 Process resource usage is collected via '''psutil''' and 
 reported to logfile and/or Graphite server 
 (http://graphite.wikidot.com/). You can dynamically add or 
 remove tracked processes. 
